channel.title: Object help [317][DELTA]
channel.description:
Hello moparscape members. I am currently working on my first project SiborScape. I have been trying to add objects. I was able to get the ancient altar and prayer altar to show but I can't get stalls or portals to show.
I am coding from a blank source.
This code is where I have put my objects: [code]// ************************************************** Start All Objects!!! ************************************************** \\ public void NewObjects() { makeGlobalObject(3091, 3506, 6552, -2, 10); //Ancient Altar makeGlobalObject(3095, 3506, 409, -2, 10); //Prayer Altar makeGlobalObject(4876, 3843, 4874, -2, 10); //Crafting Stal makeGlobalObject(4876, 3843, 4875, -2, 10); //Food Stall makeGlobalObject(4876, 3843, 4876, -2, 10); //General Stall makeGlobalObject(4876, 3843, 4877, -2, 10); //Magic Stall makeGlobalObject(2156, 3489, 2273, -2, 10); // Donator Zone Tele makeGlobalObject(2156, 3488, 2273, -2, 10); // Staff Zone Tele } // ************************************************** End All Objects!!! ***************************************************** \\[/code]
Much appreciated, Sibor
